                                                                                              CM-11(02)       USER-INSTALLED SOFTWARE | SOFTWARE INSTALLATION WITH PRIVILEGED STATUS
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              CM-11(02)             user installaon of soware is allowed only with explicit privileged status.

